Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, you and I still haven’t settled the score yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can call this the {\i1}real{\i0} Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I'm gonna bring it to ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Up until now, I've been fighting as\N a Numbers Hunter for Haruto's sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I definitely won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, my whole body's kinda tingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we met him that first time, we came really close to getting taken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I turned into ZeXal with you, when we were fighting him inside the Emperor's Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also had a Tag Duel to save Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all of that, I really started to think Kaito was a strong guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how much I may think of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my only goal is to surpass him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with you, I will beat him for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma is bursting with fighting spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting somewhat nervous myself, or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0} win against Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No clue, but this is the true Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! It's Yuma we're talking about,\N so he'll definitely win, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meo-what's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:02:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the mood you guys are in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}, will you please teach that Yuma dork a lesson?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, I'll finally settle this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our Duelist's pride at stake, we will challenge you and win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my full strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I accept this fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Mode: Photon Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision: Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:05:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too soon for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-\N- Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't leave here until he's lost, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(522,509)}"Number 72: The Ultimate Showdown Has Come!!\N Yuma VS Kaito: The Other W.D.C. Final!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, you too! Don't look so grumpy and do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! Don't tell me, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can {\i1}see{\i0} this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's become visible to me somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(634,515)}Apparently, due to the effects of that battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(634,514)}there are a few people that have become able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,520)}Does that mean that Shark and Kaito, too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Astral, Yuma? Don't you want to come at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Here I go. I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Ganbara Knight in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy... Even though Ganbara Knight switches to Attack Mode when it's attacked...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, Summoning a zero Attack Power Monster in Attack Position is just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just do your best, Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Continuous Magic, Zerozelock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the effect of this card,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters on the field with zero Attack Points can't be attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's Kaito, we have to assume there's a good chance he'll bring out Galaxy-Eyes from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with the effect of Ganbara Knight, this is a double solution to face the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I end my turn with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now bring it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma, you certainly have become stronger...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I have no Monsters on my field, I can Special Summon this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear, Photon Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Normal Summon Photon Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Monsters with more than 2000 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even knowing the defense we set up, he still went and Summoned them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I release my 2000 Attack Power Photon Crusher and my 2100 Photon Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness within the shining galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become the light of hope and live as my servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incarnation of light descends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be buried in the Galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy-Eyes, attack Ganbara Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the effect of Zerozelock, you can't attack my zero Attack Power Ganbara Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Quick-Play Magic, Galaxy Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, by halving the Attack Power of my Galaxy-Eyes until the end of the turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can negate the effects of up to two face-up cards on the opponent's field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ganbara Knight's Monster Effect and Zerozelock's effect are sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As to be expected from Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had already thought a step ahead of us when he Summoned Galaxy-Eyes, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy-Eyes, attack Ganbara Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Stream of Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1500 damage all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's still no match for Kaito, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's me-ot the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Yuma, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I know... that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito! The Duel has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's always like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You always stand up again and again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Looking forward...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Continuous Magic, Battle Gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, when a player controls a Monster that did not battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will receive 1000 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa... Wait a sec! What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have no other option but to battle against Galaxy-Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effect of Galaxy Burst ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy-Eyes Attack Power and the effect of Yuma's Zerozelock return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you struggle, it won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I expect a Duel with you to be like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This happens and that happens and on it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that totally fun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about my tactics are fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the throbbing of our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The throbbing of our hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that throbbing is in a Duel, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I Duel, I understand how amazing my opponent is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That throbbing spread and gathered everyone here together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throb it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mood is unbeatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the throbbing too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from Yuma's and Kaito's Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throbbing of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have this throbbing, everyone will become your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You become one in a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, don't you think that too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then show me your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My true victory will be defeating your Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, call the Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll show it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Goblindbergh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Goblindbergh is Summoned successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon a Level Four or lower Monster from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay my Level Four Goblindbergh and Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use these two Monsters to build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Number 39! Aspiring Emperor - Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor - Hope attacks Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cat{\i0}! But meo-why, when Hope has the lower Attack Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detach one Overlay Unit to negate Hope's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're aiming at, but did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the effect of Battle Gravity, because you didn't battle, you take 1000 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Quick-Play Magic, Flash Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster Effect is activated during battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it increases the Attack Power of one Monster by 800 points,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and negates the effects of all Monsters on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Galaxy-Eyes' effect is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't Banish Monsters anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope's Attack Power goes up to 3300!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the Monster Effects of both Galaxy-Eyes and Aspiring Emperor - Hope are negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the effect, Galaxy-Eyes cannot Banish Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Hope's effect never negated the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means, I increase its Attack Power and the battle continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy-Eyes' effect is held off too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aspiring Emperor - Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Battle Simulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When two Monsters battle, both their Attack Points are halved, and they will not be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he managed to minimize the Battle Damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His spirit's not too shabby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Quick-Play Magic, Bi-Bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be activated by targeting a Monster on my field who had its Attack Power decreased!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster's Attack Power is doubled during the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the effect of Battle Simulation is negated, and the opposing Monster can be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean... Galaxy-Eyes will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hope! Big Hope Sword Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effects of all Magic and Traps ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Hope's Attack Power and effect goes back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to inflict huge damage on Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}How was it? How was it, Astral?!\N Wasn't it awesome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}I'm awesome, aren't I?! Aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how often he fails...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times he gets in a jam...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never gives up, desperately trying to stand up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and he enjoys Dueling from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, you can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother... I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer... keep Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you can't keep Dueling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...find any meaning in continuing to Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, I've only been Dueling for Haruto's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that Haruto has been saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my reason to fight has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a break! You have been my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you just quit like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, unlike you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give a passionate Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, that's where you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma is fighting with me to collect the Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory will bring back my lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is nothing but collecting the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling with Yuma brought something much more important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through Dueling, you are talking from heart to heart, deepening the bonds between your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, the same applies to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, you are a very important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories are things of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends represent the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be tied to the past anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, besides, haven't you already noticed this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it this why you have come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All Duelists really are friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}It lets one change themselves and bring it on a whole new level!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I promised Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swore to let him see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kite it to 'em, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel your throbbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your throbbing isn't this weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to it than that! Much more! So show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your own Kite it to 'em within you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, this is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the expectations of us adults, I repeatedly made Kaito suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see in my brother's eyes that he's trying to respond to Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This throbbing won't satisfy anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what lies ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I will open up my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My own Dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Kaito got his own Dueling back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo, you really are a remarkable guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma's son, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's head back to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chris...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thomas...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, I'm certain that we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, come on, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come! My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:23:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During our clash with our old nemesis Kaito,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a back-and-forth Duel commences with both sides using their full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will the Goddess of Victory smile upon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Kaito when he's serious! If we let our guard down for a moment, we'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, let's come at him with all we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using the same strategy I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.74,0:24:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Dream Grand Clash!\N Double Hope vs Double Galaxy-Eyes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll both bring it to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal powers up this October!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A new enemy has come from the Barian World!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.90,0:24:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The title will be "Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal II!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It starts broadcasting October 7th, 5:30 PM!

